                        <h3><li>Using Pick-C app</li></h3>
                        <b>1.1 Downloading the App</b>
                        <p>Pick-C App is available to download using app store provided in your mobile. The Pick-C app supports the following devices and versions of the operating system:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Android - v5.0 and above</li>
                            <li>Apple IOS </li>
                        </ul>

                        You can also download the Pick-C app using the link below:
                        <br />
                        http://Link to download Pick-C
                        <br />
                        If you are unable to download the app, write to us at:
                        <br />
                        <a href="#">Email ID: support@pickcargo.in </a>
                        <br />
                        <br />

                        <b>1.2	Signing Up with Pick-C</b>
                        <p>
                            To start using the Pick-C app, you must sign up by providing your details such as name, mobile number, email ID, and so on. Along with these details, you must provide a unique password in order to log into the app.<br />
                            <strong>Follow these steps:</strong>
                        </p>

                        <ol>
                            <li>Open Pick-C app in your mobile.<br /><br /><img src="~/images/helpImages/signup.jpg" alt="login" /></li>
                            <br />
                            <li>
                                Tap on SIGN UP button as shown in the above screen.
                                Register screen appears.<br /><br /><img src="~/images/helpImages/register.jpg" alt="login" />
                            </li>
                            <br />
                            <li>In Full name field, enter your full name.</li>
                            <li>In Mobile number field, enter a valid mobile number. The entered mobile number must be the number you have registered.</li>
                            <li>In Email id field, enter your valid email id.</li>
                            <li>
                                In Enter password field, enter a unique password. Your password must contain minimum 8 characters with one upper case and one numeric character.
                                For example: Transport@1.
                            </li>
                            <b>Note:</b> It is recommended that your password does not contain your first or last name, mobile number.</li>
                            <li>In Re-enter password field, re-enter the password.</li>
                            <li>
                                Tap on SIGN UP button as shown in the above screen.
                                I agree screen appears, as shown below:<br /> <br /><img src="~/images/helpImages/agree.jpg" alt="Agree" />
                            </li>
                            <br />
                            <li>
                                Check I Agree check box.<br />
